Also read: `ARCHITECTURE.md`, `ROADMAP.md`, `AGENTS.md`.

## Agent behavior

- Before implementing features, check the current phase in `docs/IMPLEMENTATION_PLAN.md` and `ROADMAP.md`
- Do not skip phases (e.g. no vacancy scraping before Phase 1 auth/health is done)
- Respect locked decisions: n8n = orchestration, NestJS = business logic, Playwright = browser only, Postgres ApplyJob + n8n apply-next (no Redis/BullMQ), Playwright `storageState` auth, OpenAI-compatible LLM, Ops UI = `apps/web` read-only via Backend API
- After finishing a phase, update checkboxes in `ROADMAP.md`
- Keep changes aligned with `.cursor/rules/01-architecture.mdc`
- Current focus: Phase 0–7 complete (Ops UI + CI/CD)
